sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(User Code)
    participant Exp as AI4RAGExperiment<br/>.search()
    participant SS as SearchSpace<br/>Manager
    participant HPO as GAM Optimizer<br/>(or Random)
    participant Chunker as LangChain<br/>Chunker
    participant Embed as Embedding Model<br/>(LS/OpenAI)
    participant VS as Vector Store<br/>(LS/Chroma)
    participant Ret as Retriever
    participant FM as Foundation Model<br/>(LS/OpenAI)
    participant Eval as Unitxt<br/>Evaluator
    participant LS as Llama Stack<br/>Server
    participant EH as Event Handler<br/>(Local/KFP)

    Note over User,EH: Flow 1: RAG Optimization Experiment

    User->>Exp: search(rag_template, search_space, budget)
    Exp->>SS: prepare_search_space()
    SS->>LS: GET models.list()<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Key
    LS-->>SS: Available models list
    SS-->>Exp: Prepared search space<br/>(with constraints applied)

    loop For each optimization iteration (budget)
        Exp->>HPO: suggest_next_params()
        HPO-->>Exp: Parameter configuration

        Note over Exp,VS: Index Phase
        Exp->>Chunker: chunk(documents)
        Chunker-->>Exp: Document chunks
        Exp->>Embed: embed(chunks)
        Embed->>LS: POST embeddings API<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Key
        LS-->>Embed: Embedding vectors
        Embed-->>Exp: Embedded chunks
        Exp->>VS: insert(chunks, embeddings)
        VS->>LS: POST vector_io.insert<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Key
        LS-->>VS: Insertion confirmed

        Note over Exp,FM: Retrieve + Generate Phase
        Exp->>Ret: retrieve(query)
        Ret->>VS: similarity_search(query)
        VS->>LS: POST vector_io.query<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Key
        LS-->>VS: Relevant chunks
        VS-->>Ret: Retrieved context
        Ret-->>Exp: Context documents
        Exp->>FM: generate(query, context)
        FM->>LS: POST chat.completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Key
        LS-->>FM: Generated answer
        FM-->>Exp: RAG answer

        Note over Exp,Eval: Evaluation Phase
        Exp->>Eval: evaluate(answer, reference)
        Eval-->>Exp: Metrics (correctness,<br/>faithfulness, context)<br/>with confidence intervals

        Exp->>HPO: observe(params, score)
        Exp->>EH: emit(evaluation_record)
    end

    Exp-->>User: Best RAG Pattern<br/>(optimal parameters)

    Note over User,EH: Flow 2: Models Pre-Selection (MPS)

    User->>Exp: search(mps_config=...)
    Exp->>SS: ModelsPreSelector.run()
    SS->>LS: GET models.list()<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Key
    LS-->>SS: All available models

    loop For each model pair
        SS->>Embed: embed(benchmark_docs)
        Embed->>LS: POST embeddings<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Key
        LS-->>Embed: Vectors
        SS->>VS: insert into ChromaDB<br/>(in-memory)
        SS->>FM: generate(query, context)
        FM->>LS: POST chat.completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, API Key
        LS-->>FM: Answer
        SS->>Eval: evaluate(answer, ref)
        Eval-->>SS: Score
    end

    SS-->>Exp: Top-N model pairs<br/>(reduced search space)
